# Vision-RCP Global Ignore Rules

# Python
**/__pycache__/
**/*.py[cod]
**/*.so
**/.venv/
**/venv/
**/env/
**/build/
**/dist/
**/*.egg-info/

# Node.js (UI)
**/node_modules/
**/dist/
**/dist-ssr/
**/*.local
**/package-lock.json

# Vision-RCP Specific
**/.vision-rcp/
**/*.log
**/*.db
**/*.port
**/*.md
!README.md
status.json
bridge_status.json

# Secrets & Environment
**/.env
**/.env.local
**/.env.*.local
**/secrets.json
**/config.toml

# OS Files
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db
